# Get trader information
<%= partial 'documentation/partials/google_tag_manager_js' %>
Use the POST endpoint [Get information relating to an excise trader](/api-documentation/docs/api/service/excise-movement-control-system-api/1.0/oas/page#tag/Traders/operation/pre-validate-trader) to get information about an excise trader.

## Request body schema

Full details of the request body schema can be found in the [API reference](/api-documentation/docs/api/service/excise-movement-control-system-api/1.0/oas/page#tag/Movements/operation/pre-validate-trader).

The request body must include the Excise Id and authorisation request. Optionally, you can include the entity group and products list.

### Entity groups

The following entity groups are available:

- UK Record
- EU Record
- UK Temporary Authorisation
- EU Temporary Authorisation

## Responses 

Full details of successful and unsuccessful responses and their schema can be found in the [API reference](/api-documentation/docs/api/service/excise-movement-control-system-api/1.0/oas/page#tag/Movements/operation/pre-validate-trader) on the HMRC Developer Hub.

| Response code | Status | Details | Contents | 
| -- | -- | -- | -- |
| 200 | Successful   | Validation performed successfully                                                  | Processing date and time, Excise Id, Validation result  |
| 200 | Successful   | Validation performed with a business error (invalid trader, invalid product codes) | Processing date and time, Excise Id, Validation result, fail details (valid trader, error code, error text and validate product authorisation response) |
| 400 | Unsuccesful  | Invalid JSON or mandatory fields missing                                           | Processing date and time, message   |
| 500 | Unsuccessful | Internal server error                                                              | Processing date and time, messages  |

### Trader types

The following error codes / error text are available:

1. Pending
2. Expired
3. Withdrawn
4. Cancelled
5. Used
6. Not found